{"tid":1786113,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"珍惜眼前人","createTime":"2019-12-17T02:00:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T13:28:07.000Z","uid":41176,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5369e427db3d789b7a2d0a45d32a708bb2502749","tid":1786113,"uid":41176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T02:00:12.000Z","msg":"分手就快兩年<br />\n最近起身發覺夜晚個夢都係同ex以前嘅事<br />\n或者有啲未見過嘅故事，但係同ex 一齊過<br />\n坐起身之後諗明明所有嘢都咁真實<br />\n但其實上次見佢已經係差唔多兩年前<br />\n<br />\n之前有次出街發夢<br />\n夢見幾粒子彈喺自己個頭側邊飛過<br />\n生死一刻諗起嘅係如果有咩事喺醫院會唔會見到佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當初分手都係因為自己唔識珍惜<br />\n唔識欣賞佢為自己付出嘅每件事<br />\n覺得好多嘢係理所當然<br />\n連比返同樣嘅關心佢都做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望依家有愛嘅人，有緊張嘅家人嘅你哋<br />\n記得多啲同佢哋講聲你愛佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到佢哋嘅時候比返個攬攬佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n愛有時都係要講出口㗎<br />\n<br />\n依家咩事都有機會發生<br />\n唔知下一秒消失嘅會唔會係自己<br />\n後悔嘅時候所有事都已經太遲㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n光復香港之前<br />\n定係光復香港之後<br />\n都唔可以忘記你身邊所愛嘅嗰一個人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OxY1uA1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOxY1uA1.jpg&h=7abca60c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c1OEgf2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc1OEgf2.jpg&h=41af048b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a790a97fa8622ab71bccf516065ef73580b69a7e","tid":1786113,"uid":171094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T02:02:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24dcff12cf9a18d04c44ca739af6494cc3b40bea","tid":1786113,"uid":41176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T02:13:03.000Z","msg":"聖誕節記得一齊出嚟和你Shop <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b970470e02d7c2e4ea9d991b0bfd2248a89d82cb","tid":1786113,"uid":4176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T04:57:11.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05876acb6c134209e57e9099d0e45f084579b360","tid":1786113,"uid":41176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b970470e02d7c2e4ea9d991b0bfd2248a89d82cb","tid":1786113,"uid":4176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T04:57:11.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T06:59:02.000Z","msg":"頂帽嘅色<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b233eb1f2219a373f3f275a347fd0545fdcedd0","tid":1786113,"uid":41176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T06:59:14.000Z","msg":"自拉"},{"pid":"d814797eec73cf966bff69c4a261abc3406f45a4","tid":1786113,"uid":335891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T09:05:28.000Z","msg":"愛有時係要講出口 真<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5928e7f31435e1a88a7a8dfa4ebc86832468e706","tid":1786113,"uid":41176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d814797eec73cf966bff69c4a261abc3406f45a4","tid":1786113,"uid":335891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T09:05:28.000Z","msg":"愛有時係要講出口 真<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T14:13:03.000Z","msg":"真㗎<br />\n有時你以為自己咁做已經係<br />\n但其實對方未必感受到"},{"pid":"7e0143e42c0218827a0dbbad41eb76b2650594fa","tid":1786113,"uid":335891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5928e7f31435e1a88a7a8dfa4ebc86832468e706","tid":1786113,"uid":41176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d814797eec73cf966bff69c4a261abc3406f45a4","tid":1786113,"uid":335891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-1